text: Ana'ma higeno'a Filistia kumate kva vahe'mo'za ana a'te e'za amanage eme hu'naze, Samsonina inampi hanave'a me'nefi masavenke hunka revatga hugeno negasamino, inankna huta azerita anakigahumpi kasamina azerita anakimneno. Hagi e'inama hananketa magoke magokemota 1tausen 100'a silva zago kamitere hugahune.
